import React from "react";
import Header from "../../components/HomeHeader";
import Hero from "./sections/Hero";

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <main className="relative">
      <section className>
        <Header />
      </section>
      <section className>
        <Hero />
      </section>
      <section className>
        <svg
          width="1800"
          height="200"
          viewBox="0 0 1700 200"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <g transform="rotate(-5 850 75)">
            <rect width="2000" height="5075" x="-100" y="75" fill="#50C878" />
            <text
              x="850"
              y="125"
              font-family="Arial"
              font-size="30"
              fill="white"
              text-anchor="middle"
            >
              <tspan>ActiveAura</tspan>
              <tspan dx="100">ActiveAura</tspan>
              <tspan dx="100">ActiveAura</tspan>
              <tspan dx="100">ActiveAura</tspan>
              <tspan dx="100">ActiveAura</tspan>
              <tspan dx="100">ActiveAura</tspan>
              <tspan dx="100">ActiveAura</tspan>
              <tspan dx="100">ActiveAura</tspan>
            </text>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </section>
    </main>
  );
};

export default Home;
